ahr al-Ulloum]]|as=Acting President of the [[Iraqi Governing Council|Governing Council of Iraq]]}}\n|-\n{{s-ppo}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Ahmed Hassan al-Bakr]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Leader of the [[Ba'ath Party (Iraqi-led faction)|Ba'ath Party]]|years=1979\u20132006}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Izzat Ibrahim ad-Douri]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Iraq topics}}\n{{Saddam Hussein}}\n{{IraqiPres}}\n{{IraqiPMs}}\n{{Ba'ath Party}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Saddam, Hussein}}\n[[Category:1937 births]]\n[[Category:2006 deaths]]\n[[Category:20th-century criminals]]\n[[Category:20th-century novelists]]\n[[Category:20th-century politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century executions by Iraq]]\n[[Category:21st-century novelists]]\n[[Category:21st-century politicians]]\n[[Category:Anti-Zionism in Iraq]]\n[[Category:Arab nationalists]]\n[[Category:Arabic-language novelists]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Ba'athist rulers]]\n[[Category:Burials in Iraq]]\n[[Category:Cairo University alumni]]\n[[Category:Capital punishment in Iraq]]\n[[Category:Executed Iraqi people]]\n[[Category:Executed presidents]]\n[[Category:Filmed executions in Iraq]]\n[[Category:Genocide perpetrators]]\n[[Category:Heads of government convicted of war crimes]]\n[[Category:Heads of regimes who were later imprisoned]]\n[[Category:Heads of state convicted of war crimes]]\n[[Category:Iraqi Arab nationalists]]\n[[Category:Iraqi novelists]]\n[[Category:Iraqi people convicted of crimes against humanity]]\n[[Category:Iraqi people convicted of murder]]\n[[Category:Iraqi politicians convicted of crimes]]\n[[Category:Iraqi Sunni Muslims]]\n[[Category:Male novelists]]\n[[Category:Members of the National Command of the Ba'ath Party (Iraqi-dominated faction)]]\n[[Category:Members of the Regional Command of the Arab Socialist Ba'ath Party \u2013 Iraq Region]]\n[[Category:People convicted of murder by Iraq]]\n[[Category:People executed for crimes against humanity]]\n[[Category:People executed by Iraq by hanging]]\n[[Cat