 TV Liplock]] (<small>shared with [[Colin O'Donoghue]]</small>) <small>(2015-2017)</small>\n|-\n| 2019\u2013\n|''[[This Is Us]]''\n|Cassidy Sharp\n|Recurring role (Season 4)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eonline.com/news/1069210/this-is-us-twist-the-season-4-trailer-introduces-a-new-cast-of-characters|title=This Is Us Season 4 Twist! See the Trailer & Meet the New Cast|date=August 31, 2019|website=E! Online}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Director===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n|2017\n|''Warning Lables''\n|Short<br/>Nominated - [[Tribeca Film Festival|Tribeca Film Festival Award for Best Narrative Short]]\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Sun Dogs (2017 film)|Sun Dogs]]''\n|Director, Producer, Actress<br />Won - [[Mammoth Film Festival|Mammoth Film Festival Award for Best Picture]]<br />Won - [[Mammoth Film Festival|Mammoth Film Festival Award for Grand Jury Award]]<br />Won - Savannah Film Festival Award for Best Narrative Feature\n|-\n|2018\n|''Fabled''\n|TV series\n|-\n|2019\n|''[[Euphoria (American TV series)|Euphoria]]''\n|Episode: \u201c'03 Bonnie and Clyde\u201d <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2019/05/17/hbo-drama-series-euphoria-starring-zendaya-debuts-june-16-477511/20190517hbo02/|title=Breaking News - HBO Drama Series \"Euphoria,\" Starring Zendaya, Debuts June 16|website=The Futon Critic|access-date=June 19, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Artist\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2002\n| \"Too Bad About Your Girl\"\n| [[The Donnas]]\n|\n|-\n| 2003\n| \"Shut Up\"\n| [[Nick Lachey]]\n|\n|-\n|2015\n|\"What I Want\"\n|[[Will Butler]]\n|\n|-\n|2015\n|\"Demon Days (Do It All Again)\"\n|Wild Wild Horses\n|Also director\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n|2007\n|''[[Command & Conquer 3: Tiberium Wars]]''\n|Kirce James\n|\n|}\n\n==Theatre==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Venue\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''